data.description: Beautiful Ranch townhome located in the popular Summerwoods community. This 2 Bed, 2 Bath floor plan will feel like home. Carpet is in the bedrooms while LVP wood grain flooring has been installed throughout the remainder of the home. The large living/dining area has vaulted ceilings and 6' sliding glass doors that lead out to your patio with privacy fenced back yard. The open kitchen boasts 42" espresso cabinets, breakfast bar, matching stainless steel range/oven, microwave and dishwasher. The master bedroom has an extra large walk-in lighted closet and the bathroom has a 5' wide walk-in shower.
